title: Vote for September's Marsh Athlete of the Month
text: Athlete of the Month IndyStar and Marsh® proudly present the Indiana Sports Awards Athletes of the Month. High school athletic directors and coaches from across the state nominate their top athletes each week, now you decide who's the best of the best with the Marsh® Athlete of the Month. Winners will be announced each month in print and online and will be nominees. Be sure to share on social media using #INSportsAwards.
